sect1.para:
HTTP POST http://10.20.17.1:5701/hazelcast/rest/queues/tasks <CONTENT> means Hazelcast.getQueue("tasks").offer(<CONTENT>);
and HTTP DELETE http://10.20.17.1:5701/hazelcast/rest/queues/tasks/3 means Hazelcast.getQueue("tasks").poll(3, SECONDS);
Note that you will have to handle the failures on REST polls as there is no transactional guarantee.
